1
00:01:08,719 --> 00:01:09,760
Son.

2
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:14,239
Are you okay?

3
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:15,159
I'm fine.

4
00:01:16,159 --> 00:01:17,040
Thank goodness.

5
00:01:17,439 --> 00:01:18,079
Thank goodness you're okay.

6
00:01:19,319 --> 00:01:19,799
How about you two?

7
00:01:20,439 --> 00:01:21,200
I'm okay.

8
00:01:21,519 --> 00:01:22,879
Yifan and Li Yao saved us.

9
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:24,799
What about the kidnappers?

10
00:01:25,439 --> 00:01:26,480
The police took them away.

11
00:01:26,920 --> 00:01:27,920
Good.

12
00:01:33,079 --> 00:01:34,200
Let's go find Daddy, okay?

13
00:01:34,239 --> 00:01:34,719
Okay.

14
00:01:35,319 --> 00:01:35,920
Let's go.

15
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:38,359
Come on.

16
00:01:38,760 --> 00:01:39,400
Let's go.

17
00:02:02,079 --> 00:02:03,280
Uncle

18
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:09,680
You're awake

19
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,039
Later,

20
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:12,479
when the police come

21
00:02:12,719 --> 00:02:13,680
to take your statement,

22
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:16,319
about what to say and what not to say,

23
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,240
you'd better think it through.

24
00:02:19,479 --> 00:02:19,919
Uncle

25
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,280
What do you mean?

26
00:02:23,039 --> 00:02:24,159
You want me to take the fall again?

27
00:02:24,719 --> 00:02:25,439
My whole life

28
00:02:25,439 --> 00:02:26,479
has been ruined by all of you

29
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,240
So what do you want?

30
00:02:29,199 --> 00:02:30,159
From start to finish

31
00:02:30,599 --> 00:02:32,199
you and Fang Bing forced me into this

32
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,400
Li Yao

33
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,039
Don't you forget

34
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:42,800
who gave you the money

35
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,479
who paid for your mother's treatment

36
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:47,800
If I hadn't taken the fall for you

37
00:02:48,199 --> 00:02:49,879
I'd at least be a project GM by now

38
00:02:50,479 --> 00:02:52,680
with plenty to cover Mom's medical bills.

39
00:02:53,759 --> 00:02:54,240
Uncle

40
00:02:55,159 --> 00:02:56,159
That's enough

41
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:59,439
I don't want to see you again

42
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:17,120
Such a great company

43
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,399
gone, just like that.

44
00:04:29,519 --> 00:04:30,439
I really didn't expect

45
00:04:30,759 --> 00:04:31,920
that in such a harmonious society,

46
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,720
Fang Bing would take such a huge risk,

47
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,279
disregarding the dignity of the law.

48
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:36,959
And you, Xiao Yifan.

49
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,439
You knew something was going to happen.

50
00:04:38,439 --> 00:04:39,240
Why didn't you call the police right away?

51
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,839
You think you're Iron Man?

52
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,199
Chairman Zheng, you're right.

53
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,079
It was an emergency, I...

54
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:44,879
You what?

55
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:46,360
Do you have any idea,

56
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,279
if something had happened to you,

57
00:04:47,279 --> 00:04:48,360
how would I face your master?

58
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,319
It won't happen again.

59
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,800
There won't be a next time.

60
00:04:53,279 --> 00:04:53,680
I...

61
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:55,839
Has Fang Bing been caught?

62
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:56,800
He won't get away.

63
00:04:57,399 --> 00:04:59,120
The police will use Sky Net to track him.

64
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,120
Tell you what,

65
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,480
I'll give you two days off.

66
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:02,439
Go home and rest.

67
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:04,120
Chairman Zheng, that's not necessary.

68
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,160
I still have a lot of work to finish.

69
00:05:07,079 --> 00:05:08,319
Not bad, kid.

70
00:05:09,199 --> 00:05:10,160
So for Plot No. 7,

71
00:05:10,319 --> 00:05:11,480
the Phase One general contract,

72
00:05:11,639 --> 00:05:12,680
how do you plan to handle it?

73
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:14,000
I was just about to discuss it with you.

74
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,480
The bidders for Plot 7's general contract

75
00:05:15,519 --> 00:05:16,560
need to be screened further.

76
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,399
No need to discuss it. Go handle it.

77
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,160
Yes, Chairman Zheng.

78
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:27,439
I wasn't wrong about him. He's a good kid.

79
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:32,120
Why'd you call me? Out with it.

80
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,399
I found a promising talent.

81
00:05:34,399 --> 00:05:35,639
My apprentice, Xiao Yifan.

82
00:05:36,079 --> 00:05:37,399
He learns fast and works hard.

83
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:39,000
And most importantly, he's got integrity.

84
00:05:39,079 --> 00:05:41,759
He reminds me of you back in the day.

85
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:44,879
You're smooth now, trying to flatter me.

86
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,879
The thing is, construction work is too tough,

87
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:48,759
and the pay isn't great.

88
00:05:49,319 --> 00:05:51,480
I want him to join your real estate firm.

89
00:05:51,879 --> 00:05:53,959
Don't worry, I trust your judgment.

90
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:55,959
Then you'd better take good care of him.

91
00:05:56,759 --> 00:05:57,800
I was thinking...

92
00:05:58,079 --> 00:05:59,040
Don't pull strings for him.

93
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,279
Have him submit his resume directly.

94
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,680
As long as he makes it to the final round,

95
00:06:01,959 --> 00:06:02,879
I'll talk to him personally.

96
00:06:03,959 --> 00:06:04,519
Thank you.

97
00:07:17,519 --> 00:07:19,439
President Su, did you need something?

98
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,959
I'd like to have a proper talk with you.

99
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,040
This isn't the office.

100
00:07:25,399 --> 00:07:26,800
If it's not about work,

101
00:07:27,199 --> 00:07:28,279
then there's no need to say anything.

102
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,759
I know Fang Bing did many wrong things.

103
00:07:33,319 --> 00:07:34,839
But he has no education,

104
00:07:35,199 --> 00:07:36,680
and he acts without thinking.

105
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:38,160
But I really want to apologize for him,

106
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:40,199
to you and He Junjie's family.

107
00:07:42,839 --> 00:07:44,000
You don't need to apologize to me.

108
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:46,480
Everyone must pay for their own mistakes.

109
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:48,839
If that's all, I'll be going.

110
00:07:49,879 --> 00:07:50,360
Yang Hui.

111
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,439
What's with the act?

112
00:07:52,399 --> 00:07:53,759
Talking in that snide tone.

113
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,519
President Su,

114
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:57,759
please watch your words.

115
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,160
You really know how to put on an act.

116
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,560
No wonder Xiao Yifan loved you for so many years.

117
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,079
You clearly saw last time

118
00:08:04,079 --> 00:08:05,000
that he had his arm around my waist.

119
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,839
And the hickey I left on his neck.

120
00:08:06,839 --> 00:08:08,279
Yet you weren't the least bit angry.

121
00:08:08,839 --> 00:08:09,959
What on earth does he see in you?

122
00:08:09,959 --> 00:08:10,839
Su Yuanyuan, that's enough.

123
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:13,680
No brand can hide your inner trashiness.

124
00:08:14,079 --> 00:08:15,439
I have nothing to do with you.

125
00:08:15,879 --> 00:08:16,759
As for what your husband did,

126
00:08:16,759 --> 00:08:17,560
those heinous things,

127
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:18,920
do you really not know?

128
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:32,440
Xiao Yifan,

129
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:33,879
It's due to your romantic entanglements.

130
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,919
That's what you get for not doing your homework.

131
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,320
Mom.

132
00:08:58,240 --> 00:09:00,480
Honey, are you not feeling well?

133
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:11,200
No fever either, so what's wrong?

134
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,879
I'd actually like to ask you,

135
00:09:13,879 --> 00:09:16,759
what's going on with you and Su Yuanyuan?

136
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:20,200
What about Su Yuanyuan?

137
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:22,559
You don't know what's up with Su Yuanyuan?

138
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,320
Fang Bing is now a wanted man.

139
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:26,000
I'm planning to give you your freedom back.

140
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:29,000
You can openly comfort her from now on.

141
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,759
Honey.

142
00:09:35,759 --> 00:09:37,600
What nonsense are you talking about?

143
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:39,519
Someone's quite jealous in here.

144
00:09:41,039 --> 00:09:42,639
Cut the smart talk.

145
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:46,240
If you don't explain yourself today,

146
00:09:46,679 --> 00:09:47,440
then from now on,

147
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,759
we're through.

148
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:52,320
That woman Su Yuanyuan,

149
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:53,879
what did she say to you this time?

150
00:09:55,679 --> 00:09:57,759
You knew she came to see me.

151
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,879
Did she discuss it with you beforehand?
